# ============================================
# 主目录仓库：默认忽略所有，只同步下面列出的
# ============================================
# 先忽略根目录下全部
/*

# --------------------------------------------
# 必须保留：否则 .gitignore 本身不会被跟踪
# --------------------------------------------
!.gitignore

# --------------------------------------------
# 配置与脚本（按需取消注释）
# --------------------------------------------
!.bashrc
!.profile
!.bash_logout
!*.sh

# --------------------------------------------
# 文档与说明
# --------------------------------------------
!sync-to-github-guide.md

# --------------------------------------------
# 目录：取消注释即同步该目录及子目录
# 只写 !目录名/ 即可，Git 会跟踪其中文件
# --------------------------------------------
# !Documents/
# !Desktop/
# !catkin_ws/
# !ros2_ws/
# !copyyy/
# !cartographer_ws/
# !ws_livox/
# !Livox-SDK2/
# !ncnn/
# !opencv-4.6.0/
# !rosdep-fix/

# --------------------------------------------
# 以下始终忽略（即使上面有规则也不跟踪）
# --------------------------------------------
.ssh/
.bash_history
.gnupg/
.cache/
.config/
.local/
.vscode-server/
.cursor-server/
.cursor/
.nx/
.ros/
.rviz/
.rviz2/
.qt/
.dbus/
.gazebo/
.ignition/
.sdformat/
.mozilla/
.dotnet/
.viminfo
.python_history
.Xauthority
.wget-hsts
.sudo_as_admin_successful
